{"service_name": "Cyber Defence Operations \u2013 1st Responder Host, Malware and Network Forensic Training", "service_id": "6622673551491072", "company_name": "NCC Services Limited. Trading as NCC Group.", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     NCC Services Limited. Trading as NCC Group.\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Cyber Defence Operations \u2013 1st Responder Host, Malware and Network Forensic Training\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    NCC Group offers a unique one-day first-responder training course which can provide your staff with the necessary skills to ensure that they are following the correct procedures recognised by a court of law.  This is supported by custom training created to provide your team with 1st responder skills in Malware-and-Network-forensics\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Forensics Host 1st responder training\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Malware initial-triage-training - Bespoke training-to-the organisational needs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Network-logging and Network-Forensics training - Bespoke-training to-the organisational needs\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Identify data-sources which may-be encountered during a digital-forensic-investigation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Show an-understanding of-the-legal-issues surrounding digital-evidence-collection.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Explain the principles of evidence handling\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Maintain the custody chain of evidential items\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Demonstrate the ability to acquire static and volatile data\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Gaining an-understanding of-how-to-gather evidence in a forensically-sound-manner\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reducing the-costs-of-an investigation-by-allowing in-house staff-to-collect relevant-data\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Enhance the investigation process by securing volatile data\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a31200 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Termination costs apply\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/579474/6622673551491072-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/579474/6622673551491072-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/579474/6622673551491072-terms-and-conditions.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n    